<br>
After about 120 MR forget it.<br>
<br>
With 170-200 MR I can't remember ever having been snared, even when malo'd or Tash'd from an enchanter.<br>
<br>
The swam series isn't bugged, its as it should be, it has a set chance of being resisted irrelavent of your MR, the only time it will always be resisted is if a mob is flagged as being MR.<br>
<br>
A level 14 druid will land there dot on a 60 druid.<br>
<br>
The same goes for necro MR based DoT's, Boil Blood, Vexin and Splurt.<br>
